      <title>随着伊朗威胁缓解，以色列将焦点重新转向哈马斯和拉法</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/israel-turns-focus-back-to-hamas-and-rafah-as-iran-threat-eases</link>
      <description><![CDATA[以色列正将重点转向消除其所说的哈马斯在加沙的最后一个据点——再次引起国际社会对在加沙地带南部避难的约一百万平民命运的担忧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/israel-turns-focus-back-to-hamas-and-rafah-as-iran-threat-eases</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 14:45:56 GMT</pubDate>
