      <title>挪威各方考虑“大幅”增加对乌克兰的援助</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/norway-parties-considering-significant-boost-to-ukraine-aid</link>
      <description><![CDATA[外交部长埃斯彭·巴特·艾德 (Espen Barth Eide) 表示，挪威各方正在考虑“大幅”增加该国对乌克兰的 750 亿克朗（68 亿美元）长期援助。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-04-22/norway-parties-considering-significant-boost-to-ukraine-aid</guid>
      <pubDate>Mon, 22 Apr 2024 14:13:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
